## Build a phylogenetic tree using the mashtree tool based on whole genome sequences
## Input: All genome files in .fa format in the current directory
## Output: Phylogenetic tree file tree.dnd in Newick format

# -numcpus 30: Specify using 30 CPU cores for parallel processing to accelerate computation
# *.fa: Use wildcard to match all genome files with .fa extension in the current directory
# > tree.dnd: Redirect the generated tree file output to tree.dnd (standard Newick format)


/home/lidong/Software/mashtree-1.4.6/bin/mashtree -numcpus 30 *.fa > tree.dnd

